  "title": "UniformValue",
  "description": "Value accepted by a material uniform. Scalars and small tuples auto-marshal to the appropriate `Float32Array`/`Int32Array` for the backend's uniform call. `Texture`/`RenderTexture` values are bound to texture slots starting at slot 1 — slot 0 is reserved for the drawable's own `texture`.",
